{"tid":2432367,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE中文]就快考作文嘅薯仔入嚟睇睇","createTime":"2021-03-04T09:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T04:54:42.000Z","uid":264783,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1522584480d7570cf02d30ebca9b52b799434f7","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:31:31.000Z","msg":"仲有兩個月唔夠就考中文作文喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你哋溫好書未啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟簡單整合咗啲作文筆記，去考之前睇下自己有冇犯commone mistakes 以致失分都好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n****注意以下條件只適用於記敘抒情文****<br />\n1. 貼題和恰當的篇幅分配是合格線， 從第一段開始便要貼題，不要有任何一句是偏離主題的鋪排。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.  四字詞、修辭每一段都要有，aim 5星星的話應該1-2句就有修辭便最好。最簡單常用嘅修辭包括排比、反復、比喻、誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 留意題目的時間點，可以使用倒敘、插敘等等， 但一定要讓老師清晰明白每件事情發生的次序，否則會造成老師的思緒混亂。（建議：過往-&rsaquo;現今）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 取材切勿天馬行空（e.g. 每年都轉校、 家庭關係奇異地複雜）。 在文憑試中，不太需要超凡的創意力， 只需要基於現實環境的昇華。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 盡量每一句都有情感描寫或使用修辭 （全文重心：50%故事劇情+50%情感描述）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 寫出的句子應該能夠前後呼應(後一句能呼應前一句)， 否則劇情不連貫。 全文亦需要有首尾呼應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 文章必須要有轉折(昇華的地方)， 轉折應在正文中段、不要太遲， 否則爛尾。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 寫完了結尾不代表文章的結束，必須要加入情感和期望，才能造出高分數的文章。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n9. 善用短句、短段，塑造感情和哄托氣氛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10. 常用第一人稱為主角，避免挑戰以第二人稱和第三人稱作全文的論述者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11. 改善句子流暢度：S+V+O （最基本的句法）。 不要出現兩個&ldquo;的&rdquo;， 不要混淆&ldquo;的&rdquo;和&ldquo;地&rdquo;的用法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n12. 盡早改善標點符號用錯的問題，尤其是「」的運用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面嘅內容覺得有用就記低，剩低嘅日子唔好停作文訓練，搏盡無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩問題可以係下面問，議論文我就答唔到喇，等其他高手出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29294b041c65ace4dbe232003840fa3c5028afa","tid":2432367,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"39a258ed67350867dfccc6e2c751f3c67834f022","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e29294b041c65ace4dbe232003840fa3c5028afa","tid":2432367,"uid":218353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"p"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e54e573da73ce067871ba0f154224eb370d32d7","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"大提醒：必須必須必須寫簡約大綱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作文離題及超時大忌：邊寫邊作、沒有題材、腦海空白、思緒混亂、天馬行空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解決方法： 開卷前5分鐘認真分析題目，為題目重要字眼落簡約定義以及列舉重要字眼的同義詞、四字詞， 甚至是可能用到的修辭。盡量強迫自己在5分鐘內想出貼題的寫作內容、主要角色和過渡的轉折，並將所想到的內容寫在考試卷的空白位置。<br />\n在考試期間，要經常檢閱自己是否按照大綱去寫作， 同時以大綱為基礎創作文章。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n**在考試中途突然想到精彩絕倫的情節是普遍不過的事，可以將這些情節加插在故事裏，但依然盡量不偏離大綱寫作，否則有離題的風險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abf7d771e624f3a2639546b03a23f8b9ecaec43","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3oO42O8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3oO42O8.jpg&h=4acb1cd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4694731f87ac1b5dec89db0b99e5d1d7e53d232","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5890b32243752b6faa397902184fb25922ec792d","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a547580440f003e131e38f3a7b6d411e05e90d23","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c7081c0fdbbc71d6d9423ae38c6c90dea3c79146","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"e6502a1780d40158aebaffa99b84d07efd7a6bb0","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"70799b09065a6a60b58db076a5880cea2d1073f4","tid":2432367,"uid":246133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115f1a1eb2970206ff8cd616c18689b29c20b15e","tid":2432367,"uid":246133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c12ab6f00f24b4cf35921a6bf35aa810e12eb8","tid":2432367,"uid":246133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"5542534f9ead8f45d1a763366f4ac5f3d35c3b16","tid":2432367,"uid":136441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9ae700eb708c78e4702d37e3b4bf5f07a1e6d680","tid":2432367,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"你同低賤狗汪汪有冇關係？"},{"pid":"5b48b24f601f9515b483dd569a6fdef10537956c","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ae700eb708c78e4702d37e3b4bf5f07a1e6d680","tid":2432367,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"你同低賤狗汪汪有冇關係？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個嚟？"},{"pid":"740dcf43a813f879b73c9fdaa4788fce462e5dfe","tid":2432367,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7247e78c97ae420d088913a67e717e2fe59b2fad","tid":2432367,"uid":264783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"740dcf43a813f879b73c9fdaa4788fce462e5dfe","tid":2432367,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:39:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}